Everyone Deserves Access to Great Financial Products

Our Approach

You are not defined by your credit score. Our customers with average or bad credit have several options to pay less than their base rate, which is determined by multiple factors including credit score and prior history on loans and financial decisions.
MoneyLion rewards good financial habits with multiple paths to reduce rates immediately. Engage with our community and receive some of the lowest interest rates for your current credit profile.




Choose Your Path to Lower Rates 





























Boosts 01.
With just 5 Boosts from friends and family, you can reduce your rate by as much as 50%. Getting Boosts is as simple as getting likes for a photo on Facebook. There’s no catch - it’s easy and completely free.



Repayment History 02.
As you make on-time payments with MoneyLion, you qualify for cheaper loans in the future, independent of your credit score.



Improve Your Credit03.03.
With the MoneyLion Best Rate Guarantee(TM), as you improve your credit and meet our credit criteria, we’ll always first consider you for our lowest cost loans.









